13 /*
14 * Utility library.
15 */
16#include <vstream.h>
17
18 /*
19 * Global library.
20 */
21#include <mail_conf.h>
22
23 /*
24 * External interface. Tables are defined in mail_conf.h.
25 */
26#define MAIL_SERVER_INT_TABLE 1
27#define MAIL_SERVER_STR_TABLE 2
28#define MAIL_SERVER_BOOL_TABLE 3
29#define MAIL_SERVER_TIME_TABLE 4
30#define MAIL_SERVER_RAW_TABLE 5
31#define MAIL_SERVER_NINT_TABLE 6
32#define MAIL_SERVER_NBOOL_TABLE 7
33#define MAIL_SERVER_LONG_TABLE 8
34
35#define MAIL_SERVER_PRE_INIT 10
36#define MAIL_SERVER_POST_INIT 11
37#define MAIL_SERVER_LOOP 12
38#define MAIL_SERVER_EXIT 13
39#define MAIL_SERVER_PRE_ACCEPT 14
40#define MAIL_SERVER_SOLITARY 15
41#define MAIL_SERVER_UNLIMITED 16
42#define MAIL_SERVER_PRE_DISCONN 17
43#define MAIL_SERVER_PRIVILEGED 18
44#define MAIL_SERVER_WATCHDOG 19
45
46#define MAIL_SERVER_IN_FLOW_DELAY 20
47#define MAIL_SERVER_SLOW_EXIT 21
48#define MAIL_SERVER_BOUNCE_INIT 22
49
50typedef void (*MAIL_SERVER_INIT_FN) (char *, char **);
51typedef int (*MAIL_SERVER_LOOP_FN) (char *, char **);
52typedef void (*MAIL_SERVER_EXIT_FN) (char *, char **);
53typedef void (*MAIL_SERVER_ACCEPT_FN) (char *, char **);
54typedef void (*MAIL_SERVER_DISCONN_FN) (VSTREAM *, char *, char **);
55typedef void (*MAIL_SERVER_SLOW_EXIT_FN) (char *, char **);
56
57/* Type-checked API for external use. */
58#define CA_MAIL_SERVER_INT_TABLE(v) MAIL_SERVER_INT_TABLE, CHECK_CPTR(MAIL_SERVER, CONFIG_INT_TABLE, (v))
59#define CA_MAIL_SERVER_STR_TABLE(v) MAIL_SERVER_STR_TABLE, CHECK_CPTR(MAIL_SERVER, CONFIG_STR_TABLE, (v))
60#define CA_MAIL_SERVER_BOOL_TABLE(v) MAIL_SERVER_BOOL_TABLE, CHECK_CPTR(MAIL_SERVER, CONFIG_BOOL_TABLE, (v))
61#define CA_MAIL_SERVER_TIME_TABLE(v) MAIL_SERVER_TIME_TABLE, CHECK_CPTR(MAIL_SERVER, CONFIG_TIME_TABLE, (v))
62#define CA_MAIL_SERVER_RAW_TABLE(v) MAIL_SERVER_RAW_TABLE, CHECK_CPTR(MAIL_SERVER, CONFIG_RAW_TABLE, (v))
63#define CA_MAIL_SERVER_NINT_TABLE(v) MAIL_SERVER_NINT_TABLE, CHECK_CPTR(MAIL_SERVER, CONFIG_NINT_TABLE, (v))
64#define CA_MAIL_SERVER_NBOOL_TABLE(v) MAIL_SERVER_NBOOL_TABLE, CHECK_CPTR(MAIL_SERVER, CONFIG_NBOOL_TABLE, (v))
65#define CA_MAIL_SERVER_LONG_TABLE(v) MAIL_SERVER_LONG_TABLE, CHECK_CPTR(MAIL_SERVER, CONFIG_LONG_TABLE, (v))
66#define CA_MAIL_SERVER_PRE_INIT(v) MAIL_SERVER_PRE_INIT, CHECK_VAL(MAIL_SERVER, MAIL_SERVER_INIT_FN, (v))
67#define CA_MAIL_SERVER_POST_INIT(v) MAIL_SERVER_POST_INIT, CHECK_VAL(MAIL_SERVER, MAIL_SERVER_INIT_FN, (v))
68#define CA_MAIL_SERVER_LOOP(v) MAIL_SERVER_LOOP, CHECK_VAL(MAIL_SERVER, MAIL_SERVER_LOOP_FN, (v))
69#define CA_MAIL_SERVER_EXIT(v) MAIL_SERVER_EXIT, CHECK_VAL(MAIL_SERVER, MAIL_SERVER_EXIT_FN, (v))
70#define CA_MAIL_SERVER_PRE_ACCEPT(v) MAIL_SERVER_PRE_ACCEPT, CHECK_VAL(MAIL_SERVER, MAIL_SERVER_ACCEPT_FN, (v))
71#define CA_MAIL_SERVER_SOLITARY MAIL_SERVER_SOLITARY
72#define CA_MAIL_SERVER_UNLIMITED MAIL_SERVER_UNLIMITED
73#define CA_MAIL_SERVER_PRE_DISCONN(v) MAIL_SERVER_PRE_DISCONN, CHECK_VAL(MAIL_SERVER, MAIL_SERVER_DISCONN_FN, (v))
74#define CA_MAIL_SERVER_PRIVILEGED MAIL_SERVER_PRIVILEGED
75#define CA_MAIL_SERVER_WATCHDOG(v) MAIL_SERVER_WATCHDOG, CHECK_PTR(MAIL_SERVER, int, (v))
76#define CA_MAIL_SERVER_IN_FLOW_DELAY MAIL_SERVER_IN_FLOW_DELAY
77#define CA_MAIL_SERVER_SLOW_EXIT(v) MAIL_SERVER_SLOW_EXIT, CHECK_VAL(MAIL_SERVER, MAIL_SERVER_SLOW_EXIT_FN, (v))
78#define CA_MAIL_SERVER_BOUNCE_INIT(v, w) MAIL_SERVER_BOUNCE_INIT, CHECK_PTR(MAIL_SERVER, char, (v)), CHECK_PPTR(MAIL_SERVER, char, (w))
79
80CHECK_VAL_HELPER_DCL(MAIL_SERVER, MAIL_SERVER_SLOW_EXIT_FN);
81CHECK_VAL_HELPER_DCL(MAIL_SERVER, MAIL_SERVER_LOOP_FN);
82CHECK_VAL_HELPER_DCL(MAIL_SERVER, MAIL_SERVER_INIT_FN);
83CHECK_VAL_HELPER_DCL(MAIL_SERVER, MAIL_SERVER_EXIT_FN);
84CHECK_VAL_HELPER_DCL(MAIL_SERVER, MAIL_SERVER_DISCONN_FN);
85CHECK_VAL_HELPER_DCL(MAIL_SERVER, MAIL_SERVER_ACCEPT_FN);
86CHECK_PTR_HELPER_DCL(MAIL_SERVER, int);
87CHECK_PTR_HELPER_DCL(MAIL_SERVER, char);
88CHECK_PPTR_HELPER_DCL(MAIL_SERVER, char);
89CHECK_CPTR_HELPER_DCL(MAIL_SERVER, CONFIG_TIME_TABLE);
90CHECK_CPTR_HELPER_DCL(MAIL_SERVER, CONFIG_STR_TABLE);
91CHECK_CPTR_HELPER_DCL(MAIL_SERVER, CONFIG_RAW_TABLE);
92CHECK_CPTR_HELPER_DCL(MAIL_SERVER, CONFIG_NINT_TABLE);
93CHECK_CPTR_HELPER_DCL(MAIL_SERVER, CONFIG_NBOOL_TABLE);
94CHECK_CPTR_HELPER_DCL(MAIL_SERVER, CONFIG_LONG_TABLE);
95CHECK_CPTR_HELPER_DCL(MAIL_SERVER, CONFIG_INT_TABLE);
96CHECK_CPTR_HELPER_DCL(MAIL_SERVER, CONFIG_BOOL_TABLE);
